des: Want to hear some of the best Subtle Asian Jokes, but don't want to scroll for hours looking for them? Use the Subtle Asian Jokes skill to have Alexa read one off to you! You can tell Alexa 'next' to move onto the next joke or 'stop if you'd like to exit the skill. For more Subtle Asian Things, find us on Instagram at @subtleasianfeels.
